<section id="glossary" class="mt-10 pt-8 border-t border-border">
  <h2 class="m-0 mb-4 text-xs font-medium text-(--muted) uppercase tracking-wider">Glossary</h2>
  <dl class="m-0 grid gap-4">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-[3rem_1fr] gap-3 items-start">
      <dt class="m-0 font-medium"><code class="text-xs px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-muted rounded">ESM</code></dt>
      <dd class="m-0 text-(--muted) text-sm leading-relaxed">
        ECMAScript Modules. <code>type: 'module'</code> or <code>.mjs</code> entry. Native <code>import</code>/<code>export</code>.
      </dd>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-[3rem_1fr] gap-3 items-start">
      <dt class="m-0 font-medium"><code class="text-xs px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-muted rounded">dual</code></dt>
      <dd class="m-0 text-(--muted) text-sm leading-relaxed">
        Both ESM and CJS via <code>exports</code>. Works in either environment.
      </dd>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-[3rem_1fr] gap-3 items-start">
      <dt class="m-0 font-medium"><code class="text-xs px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-muted rounded">faux</code></dt>
      <dd class="m-0 text-(--muted) text-sm leading-relaxed">
        Legacy "module" field. Not true Node ESM; no <code>type: 'module'</code> or proper <code>exports</code>.
      </dd>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-[3rem_1fr] gap-3 items-start">
      <dt class="m-0 font-medium"><code class="text-xs px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-muted rounded">CJS</code></dt>
      <dd class="m-0 text-(--muted) text-sm leading-relaxed">
        CommonJS. Uses <code>require()</code>/<code>module.exports</code>.
      </dd>
    </div>
  </dl>
</section>
